<t>CREATE TABLE marketing_campaigns (
    campaign_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name TEXT NOT NULL,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,

    customer_id INT,
    ad_id INT,
    interaction_type TEXT
);

    id INT PRIMARY KEY,

    ad_content TEXT
);</t><s>INSERT INTO ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) SELECT 1, 1, 'Ad content 1' FROM dual</s>

    campaign_id INT,
    ad_content TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE interactions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    ad_id INT,
    interaction_type TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT
);</t><s>INSERT INTO ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) SELECT 1, 1, 'Ad content 1' FROM dual</s>

);

);

);

);

);

    end_date DATE
);</t><s>insert into ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) select 3, 3, 'ad content 3' from dual</s>

    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE ads (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT,
    ad_content TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE interactions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    ad_id INT,
    interaction_type TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name TEXT,
    price DECIMAL
);</t><s>INSERT INTO ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) SELECT 4, 4, 'Ad content 4' FROM dual</s>

    campaign_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE ads (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT,
    ad_content TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT
);</t><s>insert into ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) select 4, 4, 'ad content 4' from dual</s>

    customer_id INT,
    ad_id INT,
    interaction_type TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name TEXT,
    price DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE ads (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT,
    ad_content TEXT
);</t><s>insert into ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) select 4, 4, 'ad content 4' from dual</s>

    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE ads (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT,
    ad_content TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name TEXT,
    price DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE interactions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    ad_id INT,
    interaction_type TEXT
);</t><s>INSERT INTO ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) SELECT 5, 5, 'Ad content 5' FROM dual</s>

    customer_id INT,
    ad_id INT,

);

);

    campaign_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name TEXT,
    price DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE ads (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT,
    ad_content TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE interactions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    ad_id INT,
    interaction_type TEXT
);</t><s>insert into ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) select 9, 9, 'ad content 9' from dual</s>

    product_name TEXT,
    price DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE interactions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    ad_id INT,
    interaction_type TEXT
);</t><s>insert into ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) select 10, 10, 'ad content 10' from dual</s>

    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE ads (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT,
    ad_content TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE interactions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    ad_id INT,
    interaction_type TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name TEXT,
    price DECIMAL
);</t><s>INSERT INTO ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) SELECT 12, 12, 'Ad content 12' FROM dual</s>

    campaign_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT,
    ad_content TEXT
);

    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT
);</t><s>insert into ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) select 12, 12, 'ad content 12' from dual</s>

    customer_id INT,
    ad_id INT,
    interaction_type TEXT
);

    email TEXT
);

    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

    id INT PRIMARY KEY,

);

    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT,
    ad_content TEXT
);</t><s>insert into ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) select 12, 12, 'ad content 12' from dual</s>

    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE ads (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT,
    ad_content TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name TEXT,
    price DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE interactions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    ad_id INT,
    interaction_type TEXT
);</t><s>INSERT INTO ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) SELECT 13, 13, 'Ad content 13' FROM dual</s>

    customer_id INT,

);

    campaign_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name TEXT,
    price DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE ads (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT,
    ad_content TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE interactions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    ad_id INT,
    interaction_type TEXT
);</t><s>insert into ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) select 17, 17, 'ad content 17' from dual</s>

    product_name TEXT,
    price DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE interactions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    ad_id INT,
    interaction_type TEXT
);</t><s>insert into ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) select 18, 18, 'ad content 18' from dual</s>

    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE ads (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT,
    ad_content TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE interactions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    ad_id INT,
    interaction_type TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name TEXT,
    price DECIMAL
);</t><s>INSERT INTO ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) SELECT 20, 20, 'Ad content 20' FROM dual</s>

    campaign_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE ads (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT,
    ad_content TEXT
);

    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT
);</t><s>insert into ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) select 20, 20, 'ad content 20' from dual</s>

    customer_id INT,
    ad_id INT,
    interaction_type TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name TEXT,
    email TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name TEXT,
    price DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE ads (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT,
    ad_content TEXT
);</t><s>insert into ads (id, campaign_id, ad_content) select 20, 20, 'ad content 20' from dual</s>
